{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"MediaCapabilitiesInfo","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaCapabilities/encodingInfo","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Media_Capabilities_API\">Media Capabilities API <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaCapabilities\"><code>MediaCapabilities</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaCapabilities/decodingInfo\"><code>decodingInfo()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><em><code>encodingInfo()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Media Capabilities API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Screen\"><code>Screen</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaCapabilities/decodingInfo\"><code>mediaCapabilities.decodingInfo()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaCapabilities/encodingInfo\"><code>mediaCapabilities.encodingInfo()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Media_Capabilities_API\">Media Capabilities API</a>的<code><strong>MediaCapabilitiesInfo</strong></code>&nbsp;接口在&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaCapabilities\"><code>MediaCapabilities</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>接口的&nbsp; <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaCapabilities/encodingInfo\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>MediaCapabilities.encodingInfo()</code></a> 或&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaCapabilities/decodingInfo\"><code>MediaCapabilities.decodingInfo()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>&nbsp;方法返回的 promise 完成时变得可用。它提供了媒体类型是否支持，在编码或解码此媒体时是否流畅和能效等信息。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>MediaCapabilitiesInfo</code>&nbsp;接口包含 3 个布尔属性：</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code>supported</code>: 给出&nbsp;<a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>MediaConfiguration</code></a> 中定义的属性，确定指定的媒体内容能否完全被&nbsp;编码 (如果 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaCapabilities/encodingInfo\"><code>MediaEncodingConfiguration</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 已设置) 或 解码 (如果 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaCapabilities/decodingInfo\"><code>MediaDecodingConfiguration</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 已设置) 。&nbsp;如果是，<code>supported</code>&nbsp;为&nbsp;<em>true</em>. 否则为&nbsp;<em>false</em>.</li>\n <li><code>smooth</code>: 给出 <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>MediaConfiguration</code></a> 中定义的属性， 确定指定的媒体内容在回放时能否高质量和流畅。&nbsp;如果&nbsp;<code>supported</code>&nbsp;为&nbsp;<code>true</code>, 并且回放时将流畅，<code>smooth</code>&nbsp;为&nbsp;<em>true</em>, 否则为&nbsp;<em>false.</em></li>\n <li><code>powerEfficient</code>: 给出 <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>MediaConfiguration</code></a> 中定义的属性，确定指定的媒体内容在回放时能否高能效。如果&nbsp;<code>supported</code>&nbsp;为&nbsp;<code>true</code>, 并且回放时将高能效，<code>powerEfficient</code>&nbsp;为&nbsp;<em>true</em>, 否则为&nbsp;<em>false.</em></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>浏览器将报告一个支持的媒体配置为&nbsp;<code>smooth</code>&nbsp;和&nbsp;<code>powerEfficient</code>&nbsp;直到此设备的统计信息被记录。所有受支持的音频编解码器将报告为高能效。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"范例","title":"范例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// 测试的 MediaConfiguration</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> mediaConfig <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">type</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'file'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">audio</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token literal-property property\">contentType</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"audio/ogg\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token literal-property property\">channels</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token literal-property property\">bitrate</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">132700</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token literal-property property\">samplerate</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">5200</span>\n     <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 检查支持和性能</span>\nnavigator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mediaCapabilities<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">decodingInfo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>mediaConfig<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">result</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// result 包含媒体兼容信息</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'This configuration is '</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>result<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>supported <span class=\"token operator\">?</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'not '</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">'supported, '</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span>             <span class=\"token comment\">// 配置的媒体能否被用户代理解码？</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>result<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>smooth <span class=\"token operator\">?</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'not '</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">'smooth, and '</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span>               <span class=\"token comment\">// 是否流畅？</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>result<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>powerEfficient <span class=\"token operator\">?</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'not '</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">'power efficient.'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>   <span class=\"token comment\">// 是否高能效？</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/media-capabilities/#ref-for-dom-mediacapabilities-encodinginfo","title":"Media Capabilities"}],"query":"api.MediaCapabilities.encodingInfo"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"data":null,"query":"api.MediaCapabilitiesInfo","browsers":null}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参考","title":"参考","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>MediaConfiguration</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaCapabilities/encodingInfo\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>MediaCapabilities.encodingInfo()</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaCapabilities/decodingInfo\"><code>MediaCapabilities.decodingInfo()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"范例","id":"范例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参考","id":"参考"}],"summary":"Media Capabilities API的MediaCapabilitiesInfo 接口在 MediaCapabilities (en-US)接口的  MediaCapabilities.encodingInfo() 或 MediaCapabilities.decodingInfo() (en-US) 方法返回的 promise 完成时变得可用。它提供了媒体类型是否支持，在编码或解码此媒体时是否流畅和能效等信息。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"MediaCapabilities.encodingInfo()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"MediaCapabilitiesInfo","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/mediacapabilities/encodinginfo","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/mediacapabilities/encodinginfo/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaCapabilities/encodingInfo","title":"MediaCapabilitiesInfo"}],"pageTitle":"MediaCapabilitiesInfo - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}